vassal palace broke out in rebellion, the big Zhou Ban army east, Ye Mingsheng went out with the army, after experiencing several fierce battles, was ordered to garrison Ruishan County, to protect the rear of the army grain.



The Liu mansion, where he now lives, was originally the residence of a wealthy merchant in the city, which was vacated and lent to him under the coordination of the county magistrate of Ruishan.
